Thanks guys! Landry the first video was filmed Oct 10 and the second one was two Friday's ago. Went out this morning and caster for 2 hours got nothing, then jigged for 20 minutes before I had to come in and lost a nice fish almost right away.  Hopefully the weather holds up and I can get more footage this weekend.
